 *
 * @fields_start
 *
 * group:logo => Logo设置
 * logo.display => 显示Logo:select:yes|yes,no
 * logo.text => Logo文本:text:Twenty Nine Tempest
 * logo.subline => Logo副标题:text:29 Card Route
 * logo.url => Logo地址:textarea:|默认使用本地图标
 * logo.width => Logo宽度:responsive:66/72|px
 * logo.height => Logo高度:responsive:|px[可选，默认跟随宽度]
 *
 * group:navigation => 导航设置
 * navigation.display => 显示导航:select:yes|yes,no
 * navigation.bg_color => 导航背景色:color:#0b1630
 * navigation.bg_color_scrolled => 滚动后导航背景色:color:#091423
 * navigation.text_color => 导航文字颜色:color:#eaf4ff
 * navigation.link_color => 链接颜色:color:#c9d8ea
 * navigation.link_hover_color => 链接悬停颜色:color:#7be6ff
 * navigation.link_font_size => 链接字号:number:13|px
 * navigation.link_font_weight => 链接字重:number:700
 * navigation.link_gap => 链接间距:number:10|px
 * navigation.padding_x => 水平内边距:number:18|px
 * navigation.padding_y => 垂直内边距:number:12|px
 * navigation.min_height => 最小高度:number:74|px
 * navigation.box_shadow => 阴影:text:0 18px 42px rgba(2,8,20,0.28)
 * navigation.backdrop_blur => 背景模糊:number:14|px
 * navigation.use_custom_links => 使用自定义导航链接:select:yes|yes,no
 * navigation.items => 导航项:textarea:Home=>/\r\nAbout=>/about\r\nBlog=>/blog\r\nFAQs=>/faqs|每行一项，格式：标题=>链接
 * group:navigation_labels => 导航菜单显示名称（有对应页面时显示，留空使用页面标题）
 * navigation.label_home_page => 首页菜单名:text:
 * navigation.label_about_page => 关于我们菜单名:text:
 * navigation.label_blog_list => 博客菜单名:text:
 * navigation.label_contact_page => 联系我们菜单名:text:
 * navigation.label_terms_of_service => 条款菜单名:text:
 * navigation.label_privacy_policy => 隐私政策菜单名:text:
 * navigation.use_subpages => 兼容旧版-使用子页面生成导航:select:no|yes,no
 *
 * group:download_button => 下载按钮
 * download_button.display => 显示下载按钮:select:yes|yes,no
 * download_button.text => 按钮文字:text:Play Now
 * download_button.url => 按钮链接:text:#download
